    "composer": "Paulinho da Viola",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tinha eu 14 anos de idade quando meu pai me chamou</span>\n                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Perguntou-me se eu queria estudar filosofia</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Medicina ou engenharia</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tinha eu que ser doutor</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas a minha aspiração era ter um violão</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G°\">G°</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Para me tornar sambista</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ele então me aconselhou </span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">\"Sambista não tem valor, nesta terra de doutor\" </span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E seu doutor, o meu pai tinha razão </span>\n\n                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vejo um samba ser vendido, o sambista esquecido</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu verdadeiro autor</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu estou necessitado, mas meu samba encabulado</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu não vendo não senhor!</span>\n",
